Walk like an Egyptian.

349
00:22:55,010 --> 00:22:57,721
The blond waitresses take their trays

350
00:22:57,746 --> 00:22:59,817
They spin around, and they cross the floor

351
00:22:59,842 --> 00:23:01,091
They've got the moves

352
00:23:01,116 --> 00:23:02,084
Oh, whey, oh

353
00:23:02,117 --> 00:23:03,118
You drop your drink

