00:23:03,151 --> 00:23:04,619
Then they bring you more

355
00:23:04,644 --> 00:23:06,889
All the school kids so sick of books

356
00:23:06,914 --> 00:23:09,099
They like the punk and the metal band

357
00:23:09,124 --> 00:23:10,526
When the buzzer rings

358
00:23:10,551 --> 00:23:11,577
Oh, whey, oh

359
00:23:11,602 --> 00:23:13,837
They're walking like an Egyptian

